{\b0 \cf1 \f4 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa200 \sb0 
 Because ten percent of Barrister Associates\rquote  income from the tax shelter promotion exceeded $1000, the district ordered the government to reassess the penalty using the gross income method. Thus, it was only in the subsequent 1989 assessment that Barrister Associates\rquote  gross income became relevant.
